<p><span class="anchor" id="p29"></span>لَا يَبِيع مَال زيد فباه بِإِذْنِهِ حنث وَإِلَّا<a href="#p29" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p30"></span>بِأَن بَاعه بِغَيْر إِذْنه<a href="#p30" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p31"></span>فَلَا<a href="#p31" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
