<p><span class="anchor" id="p35"></span>لَا يهب لَهُ<a href="#p35" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p36"></span>أَي لزيد مثلا<a href="#p36" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p37"></span>فَأوجب لَهُ<a href="#p37" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
